    "Details": "The ER-SR-787 mounts dual ten-ton Heavy Duty Piledrivers in each arm, backed by five small lasers spread across the torso for precision work. Two five-ton cargo bays provide onsite mineral storage. Full environmental sealing and a searchlight suit it for vacuum and deep-mine operations. Jump jets in each leg aid mobility across uneven terrain. Maximum load Heavy Industrial armor covers the entire frame.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Rugged</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.91</color></b>",
